title: Introducing 'The New Washington'
description: Who are the characters remaking Washington? Michael Barbaro, the host of "The Daily," and Carl Hulse, The Times's chief Washington correspondent, discuss the key political figures that we’ll be hearing from on this show.
author: thenewwashington@nytimes.com (The New York Times)
